sequenceDiagram
    participant Script as Python Script
    participant Trace as trace("Research Planning Workflow")
    participant Runtime as Agents Runtime
    participant LLM as Research Planner Agent
    participant Tool as get_research_sources()

    Script->>Trace: Start workflow trace
    Trace->>Runtime: Run traced agent execution

    Script->>Runtime: Runner.run_sync(agent, input="learn about AI agents")
    Runtime->>LLM: Send instructions + user input + output schema + tool schema

    Note over LLM: Reads instructions and sees tool is available

    LLM-->>Runtime: Tool call: get_research_sources()
    Runtime->>Tool: Execute Python function
    Tool-->>Runtime: ["Wikipedia", "Google", "YouTube"]

    Runtime->>LLM: Return tool result
    Note over LLM: Build 5-step structured plan<br/>using only available sources

    LLM-->>Runtime: Structured JSON matching ResearchPlanModel
    Runtime-->>Script: result.final_output

    Script->>Script: print(model_dump_json(indent=2))
    Runtime-->>Trace: Record model call + tool call + final response
    Trace-->>Script: End workflow trace